Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙鲁游戏迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来能让我消遣消遣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经打倒短笛大魔王的少年救世主也许还会出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向神仙祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷也没用 神仙已经没有了






Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:02:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新任神仙\N龙珠终于复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界王 你在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布鲁斯 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界王 醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 孙悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是超级赛亚人的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然来我这儿了 打发时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道地球上发生大事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 人造人沙鲁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你周围总是接二连三地发生大事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想找个那美克星人来当新的神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样龙珠也能复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道那美克星人所在星球的方向就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能顺利找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神仙不在以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波先生很是寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那也自然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偌大的神殿 他一个人当然寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 别让我分神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A I U E O
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你认真点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 真的找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 是这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算离得远 只要知道方向总能搜寻气息的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 是瞬间移动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间移动是雅德拉克星人的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们教你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是报复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 就是这股气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是那美克星人的气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢了 界王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多短笛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大长老…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我叫孙悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是在那美克星大战弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救了我们的悟空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜那美克星爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来地球形势危机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道沙鲁肆虐的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那股邪恶之气已经传到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想找一个人去地球当神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能复活龙珠的话 那些被沙鲁杀害的人就有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们谁愿意去地球做神仙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是有个非常合适的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你儿子悟饭和小林的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从来到这里后他一直很想念地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想念悟饭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 如果不能使用龙珠的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看丹迪这样 他可是个优秀的龙族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能成为一名合格的神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教 丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就马上出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会照顾好丹迪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干啊 丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空 我们会为地球祈祷和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是地球的新任神仙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了新的那美克星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是新任神仙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪真的能胜任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就带小林和悟饭过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国观众
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个好消息告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的天才格斗家 英雄撒旦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定参加沙鲁游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是超级英雄撒旦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦 撒旦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界格斗冠军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦先生 你觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙鲁可是消灭了整支军队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些只是把戏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他事先安置好炸药 我一眼就看穿了 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得在格斗方面沙鲁就是个菜鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种虚张声势的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷一定会干掉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对 全球观众们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个无可救药的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空 你扔下我们到底去了哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 琪琪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林 悟饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带来了新任神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫丹迪的那美克星人认识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是丹迪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:10:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 你能来真好啊 丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你要在地球当神仙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就觉得你很特别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后每天都能见面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真会制造龙珠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美克星大叔告诉我丹迪是优秀的龙族呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指大长老
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就是大长老拍胸脯保证的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙珠大概100天左右能制造完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么长时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是复活以前地球上的神龙模型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:11:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些龙珠应该变成石头分散在地球各地了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神龙的模型波波也曾做过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可以像那美克星的龙珠一样实现三个愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一个愿望复活很多人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如“让被沙鲁杀害的人复活”之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样一开始做些调整就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样就只能实现两个愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能办到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 神龙的模型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波先生 把模型拿来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是波波做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣的神龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叽里咕噜 咕噜巴拉 唧唧歪歪 叽叽喳喳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下那些四散的龙珠应该都复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经复活了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然拥有出色的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找布尔玛借龙珠雷达去收集龙珠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟饭 你不用特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沙鲁游戏到来之前 你就在这里陪丹迪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空先生 我想问你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空先生看起来信心十足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是已经发现沙鲁的弱点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啊 那家伙有弱点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事 你知道吗 悟饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空先生明知赢不了沙鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没找到他的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还这么开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是让我期待着…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有胜算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只是盲目乐观呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 人造人的构造果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖罗博士虽然是个恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却是一个十足的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 布尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想借用一下龙珠雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从那美克星带来了新的神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达就在那边的抽屉里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来状态不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想问问特兰克斯的事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 真变成龙珠了啊






Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个也找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都怀着不同的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间渐渐逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来十天太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离沙鲁游戏还有几天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知悟空找齐龙珠没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下七颗龙珠就凑齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦 撒旦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦 我的明星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他 撒旦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的沙鲁 我会让你后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命运就和这辆公车一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十天转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球迎来了命运之日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要当心啊 悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟饭不会去战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我 别让悟饭战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟饭也许也要参战…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔干劲十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么安静
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张过度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空 有件糟糕的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次虽然让龙珠一次能复活很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:20:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我和悟空这样死过一次的人就无法复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先没有说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 别在意 丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不死不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手可是沙鲁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要到12点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乐平叔叔和天津饭叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过恐怕无法参战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离沙鲁游戏开始还有一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以必死的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独家给各位转播沙鲁战前的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙鲁纹丝不动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙鲁游戏的胜者究竟是怪物沙鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是信心十足的悟空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离决斗还有一个小时…





Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是和沙鲁的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后 大菜鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙由我撒旦来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会被杀的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出场还不如让我上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 龙珠改
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦军团大暴动\N沙鲁游戏开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越弱的家伙越敢说啊

